GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
HOUSE BILL 1237
RATIFIED BILL
AN ACT TO APPOINT PERSONS TO VARIOUS PUBLIC OFFICES UPON THE
RECOMMENDATIONS OF THE PRESIDENT PRO TEMPORE OF THE SENATE AND
THE SPEAKER OF THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES AND TO MAKE
CORRECTIONS TO PREVIOUS APPOINTMENTS.
Whereas, G.S. 120-121 authorizes the General Assembly to make certain
appointments to public offices upon the recommendations of the President Pro Tempore of the
Senate and Speaker of the House of Representatives; and
Whereas, the President Pro Tempore of the Senate and the Speaker of the House of
Representatives have made recommendations and technical corrections; Now, therefore,
The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
PART I. PRESIDENT PRO TEMPORE'S RECOMMENDATIONS
